{"tid":1734324,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求，缺一不可！堅持下去才能救回被捕手足！","createTime":"2019-11-18T09:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T10:02:20.000Z","uid":268548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"86120a21bff7194cfb47c96ae00ce7ea4b3a99d6","tid":1734324,"uid":268548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T09:58:02.000Z","msg":"明白尋日同今日大家都好心痛，見到理大咁多手足受傷同被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n的確，這一戰我們是輸左，但場仗仲未打完，各位手足要堅持落去，只有實現五大訴求，釋放被捕義士，先可以救返所有手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家繼續努力，吸收今次的教訓，記得要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Be Water</span></span></strong>!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n這場係持久戰，我地同黑警的武力差太遠，所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Be Water</span></span></strong>好重要！當年越戰點解可以同美國周旋咁耐，仲要係五五波，係因為打游擊丫！！唔好再打陣地救下大家，唔想再見到手足受傷同被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，我想同理大的前線手足講，你地好勇敢，唔洗驚，我地會救你地出黎，請各位善用陪審員的力量！！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"33c3214940a313e9a4ecaa524f8c6a209fdde8e9","tid":1734324,"uid":340458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:02:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}